**Owner:** Roger Daniel (APEX)
**Mission:** Autonomous AI affiliate content business. One avatar posts product videos daily, earns affiliate commissions, proves P&L, then spawns more avatars.
**Active Workspace:** `E:\KLIPAURA\` (single clean repo — all work happens here)
**Last Updated:** April 11, 2026

