## REDIS QUEUE NAMESPACE

| Queue | Direction | Purpose |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| `klip:jobs:pending` | SELECTOR → AVATAR | Product jobs awaiting video render |
| `klip:hitl:pending` | AVATAR → DISPATCH | Videos awaiting human approval |
| `klip:publish:pending` | DISPATCH → publisher | Approved videos awaiting posting |
| `klip:market:sentiment` | TRADER → SELECTOR | Market sentiment score (-1.0 to 1.0), TTL 300s |
| `klip:system:videos_per_day` | CEOAgent → scheduler | Daily video budget ceiling |
| `klip:dlq` | workers → | Dead letter queue (3 failures) |
| `klip:blacklist:{url_hash}` | DISPATCH → SELECTOR | Rejected product, TTL 7 days |

