## WHAT TO NEVER DO

- Never run `git push --force` on `main`
- Never set `IS_TESTNET=false` on KLIP-TRADER without explicit instruction
- Never set `AUTOPILOT_MODE=1` before Phase 4 validation gate passes
- Never import anything from `E:\KLIPORA\`, `E:\KLIPAURA-old-full-backup\`, `E:\KLIPAURA BACKUP\`, `E:\ARCHIVE_AND_LEGACY\` — those are archive only
- Never build a new feature while a phase validation gate is incomplete
- Never hardcode avatar credentials — always read from `data/avatars/{id}/social_config.json`
- Never cross-post — each avatar's publisher reads only its own social_config.json
- Never use WaveSpeed T2V (text-to-video) — only I2V (image-to-video)
- Never use WaveSpeed TTS — only ElevenLabs
- Never recreate infrastructure that already exists in `klipaura-core/` — import from it

